{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":569,"text":"I'm McKenna Pope. I'm 14 years old,"},{"time":3113,"text":"and when I was 13, I convinced"},{"time":5102,"text":"one of the largest toy companies,"},{"time":6832,"text":"toymakers, in the world, Hasbro,"},{"time":9235,"text":"to change the way that they marketed"},{"time":11193,"text":"one of their most best-selling products."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13319,"text":"So allow me to tell you about it."},{"time":14639,"text":"So I have a brother, Gavin."},{"time":16456,"text":"When this whole shebang happened, he was four."},{"time":18875,"text":"He loved to cook."},{"time":20388,"text":"He was always getting ingredients out of the fridge"},{"time":22606,"text":"and mixing them into these, needless to say,"},{"time":24746,"text":"uneatable concoctions,"},{"time":26135,"text":"or making invisible macaroni and cheese."},{"time":29176,"text":"He wanted to be a chef really badly."},{"time":32325,"text":"And so what better gift for a kid\nwho wanted to be a chef"},{"time":35690,"text":"than an Easy-Bake Oven. Right?"},{"time":37930,"text":"I mean, we all had those when we were little."},{"time":39773,"text":"And he wanted one so badly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41913,"text":"But then he started to realize something."},{"time":44532,"text":"In the commercials, and on the \nboxes for the Easy-Bake Ovens,"},{"time":48093,"text":"Hasbro marketed them specifically to girls."},{"time":51324,"text":"And the way that they did this"},{"time":52829,"text":"was they would only feature girls\non the boxes or in the commercials,"},{"time":55935,"text":"and there would be flowery prints all over the ovens"},{"time":58314,"text":"and it would be in bright pink and purple,"},{"time":61267,"text":"very gender-specific colors to females, right?"},{"time":64608,"text":"So it kind of was sending a message"},{"time":67193,"text":"that only girls are supposed to cook; boys aren't."},{"time":70158,"text":"And this discouraged my brother a lot."},{"time":71731,"text":"He thought that he wasn't\nsupposed to want to be a chef,"},{"time":75308,"text":"because that was something that girls did."},{"time":77165,"text":"Girls cooked; boys didn't,"},{"time":78670,"text":"or so was the message that Hasbro was sending."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81160,"text":"And this got me thinking,"},{"time":83146,"text":"God, I wish there was a way that I could change this,"},{"time":85387,"text":"that could I have my voice heard by Hasbro"},{"time":88393,"text":"so I could ask them and tell them"},{"time":90170,"text":"what they were doing wrong"},{"time":91489,"text":"and ask them to change it."},{"time":92882,"text":"And that got me thinking about a website"},{"time":94700,"text":"that I had learned about a few months prior"},{"time":96171,"text":"called Change.org."},{"time":97718,"text":"Change.org is an online petition-sharing platform"},{"time":101051,"text":"where you can create a petition and share it"},{"time":103498,"text":"across all of these social media networks,"},{"time":105781,"text":"through Facebook, through Twitter,"},{"time":107223,"text":"through YouTube, through Reddit, through Tumblr,"},{"time":108777,"text":"through whatever you can think of."},{"time":110646,"text":"And so I created a petition"},{"time":112428,"text":"along with the YouTube video\nthat I added to the petition"},{"time":115642,"text":"basically asking Hasbro"},{"time":117668,"text":"to change the way that they marketed it,"},{"time":119915,"text":"in featuring boys in the commercials, on the boxes,"},{"time":122938,"text":"and most of all creating them"},{"time":124898,"text":"in less gender-specific colors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127622,"text":"So this petition started to take off --"},{"time":131020,"text":"humongously fast, you have no idea."},{"time":134387,"text":"I was getting interviewed by\nall these national news outlets"},{"time":137776,"text":"and press outlets, and it was amazing."},{"time":141352,"text":"In three weeks, maybe three and a half,"},{"time":143968,"text":"I had 46,000 signatures on this petition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148777,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":150975,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152749,"text":"So, needless to say, it was crazy."},{"time":155126,"text":"Eventually, Hasbro themselves\ninvited me to their headquarters"},{"time":159732,"text":"so they could go and unveil"},{"time":161330,"text":"their new Easy-Bake Oven product to me"},{"time":163778,"text":"in black, silver and blue."},{"time":165634,"text":"It was literally one of the best moments of my life."},{"time":168484,"text":"It was like &amp;quot;Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory.&amp;quot;"},{"time":170527,"text":"That thing was amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172413,"text":"What I didn't realize at the time, however,"},{"time":174083,"text":"was that I had become an activist,"},{"time":176010,"text":"I could change something,"},{"time":177584,"text":"that even as a kid, or maybe \neven especially as a kid,"},{"time":180591,"text":"my voice mattered, and your voice matters too."},{"time":183421,"text":"I want to let you know it's not going to be easy,"},{"time":185022,"text":"and it wasn't easy for me,"},{"time":186438,"text":"because I faced a lot of obstacles."},{"time":189250,"text":"People online, and sometimes even in real life,"},{"time":192981,"text":"were disrespectful to me and my family,"},{"time":195893,"text":"and talked about how the whole\nthing was a waste of time,"},{"time":198524,"text":"and it really discouraged me."},{"time":199988,"text":"And actually, I have some examples,\nbecause what's better revenge"},{"time":203195,"text":"than displaying their idiocy?"},{"time":205746,"text":"So, let's see."},{"time":207535,"text":"From user name Liquidsore29 --"},{"time":210259,"text":"interesting user names we have hereâ€”"},{"time":212268,"text":"&amp;quot;Disgusting liberal moms making their sons gay.&amp;quot;"},{"time":218048,"text":"Liquidsore29, really? Really? Okay."},{"time":220803,"text":"How about from Whiteboy77AGS:"},{"time":224643,"text":"\"People always need something\nto (female dog) about.\""},{"time":228792,"text":"From Jeffrey Gutierrez:"},{"time":231082,"text":"&amp;quot;OMG, shut up. You just want money and attention.&amp;quot;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234098,"text":"So it was comments like these"},{"time":236371,"text":"that really discouraged me from\nwanting to make change in the future"},{"time":239171,"text":"because I thought, people don't care,"},{"time":241628,"text":"people think it's a waste of time,"},{"time":244034,"text":"and people are going to be disrespectful \nto me and my family."},{"time":247893,"text":"It hurt me, and it made me think,"},{"time":250316,"text":"what's the point of making change in the future?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252798,"text":"But then I started to realize something."},{"time":255455,"text":"Haters gonna hate."},{"time":257896,"text":"Come on, say it with me. One, two, three:"},{"time":259670,"text":"Haters gonna hate."},{"time":262138,"text":"So let your haters hate,"},{"time":264020,"text":"you know what, and make your change,"},{"time":265704,"text":"because I know you can."},{"time":267545,"text":"I look out into this crowd,"},{"time":268967,"text":"and I see 400 people"},{"time":271233,"text":"who came out because they wanted to know\nhow they could make a change,"},{"time":274478,"text":"and I know that you can, and all\nof you watching at home can too"},{"time":277025,"text":"because you have so much that you \ncan do and that you believe in,"},{"time":280697,"text":"and you can trade it across all these social media,"},{"time":283515,"text":"through Facebook, through Twitter, through \nYouTube, through Reddit, through Tumblr,"},{"time":286401,"text":"through whatever else you can think of."},{"time":288291,"text":"And you can make that change."},{"time":289747,"text":"You can take what you believe in"},{"time":291168,"text":"and turn it into a cause and change it."},{"time":293549,"text":"And that spark that you've been \nhearing about all day today,"},{"time":296617,"text":"you can use that spark that you have within you"},{"time":299253,"text":"and turn it into a fire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300773,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302549,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}